  "id": "019cf625-7dd3-7a72-90bd-39bc1f9f036b",
  "content": "# Docs Workflow & Interactive Knowledge Dashboard — Implementation Plan\n\n> **Status:** Active\n\n**Goal:** Implement the Docs Workflow design spec (Approach B — Full Loop) across 4 phases: metadata extensions, dashboard graphed document reader, intelligence checks, and hook enforcement.\n\n**Architecture:** Extend `EntryMetadata` with `content_role`/`source_origin` fields. Add post-filter to retrieval pipeline. Build split-panel graph+reader dashboard. Extend Reasoner with doc-specific checks. Generate enforcement hooks from `corvia.toml`.\n\n**Tech Stack:** Rust (corvia kernel/server/CLI), Preact + TypeScript (dashboard), Bash (hook scripts), TOML (config)\n\n**Spec:** `docs/decisions/2026-03-13-docs-workflow-design.md`\n\n---\n",
